022c930c18687f91,983,"In brief: “lawfully” means your processing must satisfy an Article 6 lawful basis (and, if required, an Article 9 condition), as well being lawful in more general terms; “fairly” means your processing should not lead to unjustified adverse outcomes for individuals, and should be within their reasonable expectations; and “in a transparent manner” means you must properly inform individuals about how and why you intend to process their personal data.",your processing,explicit,must,obligation,satisfy an Article 6 lawful basis,"if required , an Article 9 condition ) , as well being lawful in more general terms",personal data,True,"In brief: “lawfully” means your processing must satisfy an Article 6 lawful basis (and, if required, an Article 9 condition), as well being lawful in more general terms; “fairly” means your processing should not lead to unjustified adverse outcomes for individuals, and should be within their reasonable expectations; and “in a transparent manner” means you must properly inform individuals about how and why you intend to process their personal data.",rule_candidate,information,choice|information|scope,3,0,0,1,1,1,0,0,0,0,,,,,,
