1331c9176233b177,47645,"Such a person is the “owner” of a dangerous thing as referred to in Articles 1063 to 1067of the Croatian Civil Obligations Act (COA), and is liable for damage caused by the animal (Article 1064 COA: “The owner shall be liable for damage resulting from a dangerous thing.”",The owner,explicit,shall,obligation,be,,,True,"Such a person is the “owner” of a dangerous thing as referred to in Articles 1063 to 1067of the Croatian Civil Obligations Act (COA), and is liable for damage caused by the animal (Article 1064 COA: “The owner shall be liable for damage resulting from a dangerous thing.”",rule_candidate,payoff,choice|payoff,2,0,0,1,0,0,0,1,0,0,,,,,,
1331c9176233b177,47734,"If that person cannot be determined, the owner of the thing is presumed to be liable.",that person,explicit,can,prohibition,determined,If that person can not be determined,,True,"If that person cannot be determined, the owner of the thing is presumed to be liable.",rule_candidate,payoff,choice|payoff,2,0,0,1,0,0,0,1,0,0,,,,,,
1331c9176233b177,47788,Compensation for unlawfully caused damage A person (tortfeasor) who unlawfully causes damage to another person (victim) shall compensate the victim for the damage if the tortfeasor is culpable of causing the damage or is liable for causing the damage pursuant to law.” “§1050(1) Culpability as a basis for liability,Compensation for unlawfully caused,explicit,shall,obligation,compensate the victim,if the tortfeasor is culpable of causing the damage or is liable for causing the damage pursuant to law|pursuant to law.” “§1050(1) Culpability as a basis for liability|for the damage,,True,Compensation for unlawfully caused damage A person (tortfeasor) who unlawfully causes damage to another person (victim) shall compensate the victim for the damage if the tortfeasor is culpable of causing the damage or is liable for causing the damage pursuant to law.” “§1050(1) Culpability as a basis for liability,rule_candidate,payoff,choice|payoff,2,0,0,1,0,0,0,1,0,0,,,,,,
