1331c9176233b177,47821,"§138(1) and (3) LOA provides that where several persons may be liable for damage caused and it has been established that any of those persons could have caused the damage, compensation may be claimed from all such persons.",several persons,explicit,may,permission,be,,,True,"§138(1) and (3) LOA provides that where several persons may be liable for damage caused and it has been established that any of those persons could have caused the damage, compensation may be claimed from all such persons.",rule_candidate,payoff,choice|payoff,2,0,0,1,0,0,0,1,0,0,,,,,,
1331c9176233b177,47830,"Liability of the owner of dangerous construction or thing (1) The owner of a construction shall be liable for da mage caused as a result of particular danger arising from it due to the production, storage or transmission in the construction of energy, substances which are flammable, involve a radiation hazard or can cause combustion, or toxic, caustic or environmenta lly hazardous substances, and for damage caused as a result of particular danger arising from the construction for any other reason.",Liability of the owner of dangerous construction or thing ( 1 ),explicit,shall,obligation,be,,,True,"Liability of the owner of dangerous construction or thing (1) The owner of a construction shall be liable for da mage caused as a result of particular danger arising from it due to the production, storage or transmission in the construction of energy, substances which are flammable, involve a radiation hazard or can cause combustion, or toxic, caustic or environmenta lly hazardous substances, and for damage caused as a result of particular danger arising from the construction for any other reason.",rule_candidate,payoff,choice|payoff,2,0,0,1,0,0,0,1,0,0,,,,,,
1331c9176233b177,47831,"The owner of a thing shall be liable for damage caused as a result of particular danger arising from the thing due to its flammable, radiation, combustible, toxic, caustic or environmentally hazardous characteristics, and for damage caused as a result of particular danger arising from the thing for any other reason.",The owner of a thing,explicit,shall,obligation,be,for damage caused as a result of particular danger arising from the thing for any other reason,,True,"The owner of a thing shall be liable for damage caused as a result of particular danger arising from the thing due to its flammable, radiation, combustible, toxic, caustic or environmentally hazardous characteristics, and for damage caused as a result of particular danger arising from the thing for any other reason.",rule_candidate,payoff,choice|payoff,2,0,0,1,0,0,0,1,0,0,,,,,,
1331c9176233b177,47851,"If damage is caused resulting from characteristic of a thing constituting a major source of danger or from an extremely dange rous activity, the person who manages the source of the danger shall be liable for causing the damage regardless of his or her culpability.",the person who manages the source of the danger,explicit,shall,obligation,be,If damage is caused resulting from characteristic of a thing constituting a major source of danger or from an extremely dange rous activity,,True,"If damage is caused resulting from characteristic of a thing constituting a major source of danger or from an extremely dange rous activity, the person who manages the source of the danger shall be liable for causing the damage regardless of his or her culpability.",rule_candidate,payoff,choice|payoff,2,0,0,1,0,0,0,1,0,0,,,,,,
1331c9176233b177,47852,"A person who manages a major source of danger shall be liable for causing death, personal injury or damage to the health of the victim and for dam age to a tangi bl e object belonging to the victim, unless otherwise provided by law.",A person who manages a major source of danger,explicit,shall,obligation,be,unless otherwise provided by law|unless otherwise provided by law.,,True,"A person who manages a major source of danger shall be liable for causing death, personal injury or damage to the health of the victim and for dam age to a tangi bl e object belonging to the victim, unless otherwise provided by law.",rule_candidate,payoff,choice|payoff,2,0,0,1,0,0,0,1,0,0,,,,,,
1331c9176233b177,47857,Liability of the keeper of an animal The keeper of an animal shall be liable for damage caused by the animal.”,Liability of the keeper of an animal,explicit,shall,obligation,be,,,True,Liability of the keeper of an animal The keeper of an animal shall be liable for damage caused by the animal.”,rule_candidate,payoff,choice|payoff,2,0,0,1,0,0,0,1,0,0,,,,,,
1331c9176233b177,47861,"However, it should be borne in mind that the child remains liable, whereas AI would not be capable of liability in tort.",it,explicit,should,obligation,borne,in mind,,True,"However, it should be borne in mind that the child remains liable, whereas AI would not be capable of liability in tort.",rule_candidate,payoff,choice|payoff,2,0,0,1,0,0,0,1,0,0,,,,,,
1331c9176233b177,47864,"§1054 LAO provides for the vicarious liability of employers for the torts of their employees (persons engaged to perform economic or professi onal activities on a regular basis) where the damage was caused in relation to those economic or professional activities: “(1) If a person engages another person in the [first] person's economic or professional activities on a regular basis, that person shall be liable for any damage unlawfully caused by the other person on the same basis as for damage caused by the [first] person, if the causing of damage is related to the [first] person's economic or professional activities.”",that person,explicit,shall,obligation,be,If a person engages another person in the [ first ] person 's economic or professional activities on a regular basis,,True,"§1054 LAO provides for the vicarious liability of employers for the torts of their employees (persons engaged to perform economic or professi onal activities on a regular basis) where the damage was caused in relation to those economic or professional activities: “(1) If a person engages another person in the [first] person's economic or professional activities on a regular basis, that person shall be liable for any damage unlawfully caused by the other person on the same basis as for damage caused by the [first] person, if the causing of damage is related to the [first] person's economic or professional activities.”",rule_candidate,payoff,choice|payoff,2,0,0,1,0,0,0,1,0,0,,,,,,
1331c9176233b177,47867,"the Estonian General Part of the Civil Code (EN translation) provides for vicarious liability in civil law: “(1) A person shall be liable for the conduct of and circumstances arising from another person as if that person had him or herself been responsible for that conduct and those circumstances, if that person uses the other person on a continuous basis in his or her economic or professional acti vi ty and the conduct of and circumstances arising from the other person are related to that economic or professional activity.",A person,explicit,shall,obligation,be|been,if that person uses the other person on a continuous basis in his or her economic or professional acti vi ty and the conduct of and circumstances arising from the other person are related to that economic or professional activity,,True,"the Estonian General Part of the Civil Code (EN translation) provides for vicarious liability in civil law: “(1) A person shall be liable for the conduct of and circumstances arising from another person as if that person had him or herself been responsible for that conduct and those circumstances, if that person uses the other person on a continuous basis in his or her economic or professional acti vi ty and the conduct of and circumstances arising from the other person are related to that economic or professional activity.",rule_candidate,payoff,choice|payoff,2,0,0,1,0,0,0,1,0,0,,,,,,
1331c9176233b177,47868,(2) A person shall be liable for the conduct of and circumstances arising from another person if that person uses the other person in the performance of his or her obligations and the conduct of or circumstances arising from the other person are related to the performance of those obligations.”,A person,explicit,shall,obligation,be,if that person uses the other person in the performance of his or her obligations and the conduct of or circumstances arising from the other person,,True,(2) A person shall be liable for the conduct of and circumstances arising from another person if that person uses the other person in the performance of his or her obligations and the conduct of or circumstances arising from the other person are related to the performance of those obligations.”,rule_candidate,payoff,choice|payoff,2,0,0,1,0,0,0,1,0,0,,,,,,
1331c9176233b177,47949,"106 is caused by an u ndetermined person from among identified persons who act together or carry out a similar activity, each of those persons shall be liable for the whole of the damage, unless it is shown that a particular person cannot have caused it.",each of those persons,explicit,shall,obligation,be,unless it is shown that a particular person can not have caused it|unless it is shown that a particular person cannot have caused it.,,True,"106 is caused by an u ndetermined person from among identified persons who act together or carry out a similar activity, each of those persons shall be liable for the whole of the damage, unless it is shown that a particular person cannot have caused it.",rule_candidate,payoff,choice|payoff,2,0,0,1,0,0,0,1,0,0,,,,,,
