26250ebdfd18c6e3,114962,"29C. Liability of labour contractor and hirer employer (1) Subject to subsections (2) and (6), a labour contractor and the hirer employer to whom the labour contractor has supplied a migrant worker, shall be jointly and severally liable for – (a) the payment of the remuneration and conditions of employment of the migrant worker including his safety, health and welfare; Acts 2024 587 (b) the payment of any statutory contribution in respect of every migrant worker employed by the labour contractor in the execution of the work or service.","29C. Liability of labour contractor and hirer employer ( 1 ) Subject to subsections ( 2 ) and ( 6 ) , a labour contractor and the hirer employer to whom the labour contractor has supplied a migrant worker",explicit,shall,obligation,be|Acts 2024 587 ( b ) the payment of any statutory contribution in respect of every migrant worker employed by the labour contractor in the execution of the work or service,"Subject to subsections (2) and (6), a labour contractor and the hirer employer to whom the labour contractor has supplied a migrant worker, shall be jointly and severally liable for – (a) the payment of the remuneration and conditions of employment of the migrant worker including his safety, health and welfare; Acts 2024 587 (b) the payment of any statutory contribution in respect of every migrant worker employed by the labour contractor in the execution of the work or service.",service,True,"29C. Liability of labour contractor and hirer employer (1) Subject to subsections (2) and (6), a labour contractor and the hirer employer to whom the labour contractor has supplied a migrant worker, shall be jointly and severally liable for – (a) the payment of the remuneration and conditions of employment of the migrant worker including his safety, health and welfare; Acts 2024 587 (b) the payment of any statutory contribution in respect of every migrant worker employed by the labour contractor in the execution of the work or service.",rule_candidate,payoff,choice|payoff,2,0,0,1,0,0,0,1,0,0,,,,,,
26250ebdfd18c6e3,114965,"(3) A hirer employer who is jointly liable with a labour contractor under subsection (1) may not set up as a defence to a claim from a migrant worker seeking to recover remuneration, the fact that he has already paid to the labour contractor any sum due under the arrangement with the labour contractor.",( 3 ) A hirer employer who is jointly liable with a labour contractor under subsection ( 1 ),explicit,may,prohibition,set up,,,True,"(3) A hirer employer who is jointly liable with a labour contractor under subsection (1) may not set up as a defence to a claim from a migrant worker seeking to recover remuneration, the fact that he has already paid to the labour contractor any sum due under the arrangement with the labour contractor.",rule_candidate,payoff,choice|payoff,2,0,0,1,0,0,0,1,0,0,,,,,,
26250ebdfd18c6e3,114968,"(6) Where a labour contractor supplies a migrant worker to work with a hirer employer, the hirer employer shall be – (a) liable for any act of violence at work specified in section 114(3) and (4) of the Act; (b) liable for any accident, injury or death sustained by the migrant worker out of, and in the course of, his employment.",the hirer employer,explicit,shall,obligation,be,,,True,"(6) Where a labour contractor supplies a migrant worker to work with a hirer employer, the hirer employer shall be – (a) liable for any act of violence at work specified in section 114(3) and (4) of the Act; (b) liable for any accident, injury or death sustained by the migrant worker out of, and in the course of, his employment.",rule_candidate,payoff,choice|payoff,2,0,0,1,0,0,0,1,0,0,,,,,,
