2e020d8fa65b7349,125612,"Fines must be paid and their payment proven, through the electronic means enabled for this purpose, within the period of FIFTEEN (15) business days, counted from the date the administrative act imposing the sanction is notified.",Fines,explicit,must,obligation,paid|proven|counted,,,True,"Fines must be paid and their payment proven, through the electronic means enabled for this purpose, within the period of FIFTEEN (15) business days, counted from the date the administrative act imposing the sanction is notified.",rule_candidate,payoff,choice|payoff|scope,3,0,0,1,0,1,0,1,0,0,,,,,,
