92f27d51f32aec54,318436,"Description of benefits or rights affected by the system or the sanctions it intervenes on in the relevant cases Name and contact information of the person responsible for the implementation of the system In line with the principles of algorithmic transparency, there are a number of dimensions that the responsible entities can publish to make Artificial Intelligence systems more explainable to the public.24 This list comprises a series of system characteristics, including general aspects of the system itself, as well as information about the organization that designs and implements it.",the responsible entities,explicit,can,permission,publish,,system,True,"Description of benefits or rights affected by the system or the sanctions it intervenes on in the relevant cases Name and contact information of the person responsible for the implementation of the system In line with the principles of algorithmic transparency, there are a number of dimensions that the responsible entities can publish to make Artificial Intelligence systems more explainable to the public.24 This list comprises a series of system characteristics, including general aspects of the system itself, as well as information about the organization that designs and implements it.",rule_candidate,payoff,choice|information|payoff,3,0,0,1,1,0,0,1,0,0,,,,,,
92f4be29f030ec48,318685,"Contrary to the horror scenarios put forward by some, today's AI systems will not lead to the end of humanity They are, however, far from infallible, and come with undesirable side-effects: reproduction of stereotypes, disclosure of confidential information, violation of intellectual property rights, and so on They open up new possibilities for malicious acts, particularly cyber-attacks and disinformation They are a source of systemic risk, particularly in terms of the potential for technological concentration in the hands of a small number of countries, companies or individuals Faced with these major challenges, we cannot repeat the mistakes of the past.",we,explicit,can,prohibition,repeat the mistakes of the past,"particularly in terms of the potential for technological concentration in the hands of a small number of countries , companies or individuals Faced with these major challenges",AI systems,True,"Contrary to the horror scenarios put forward by some, today's AI systems will not lead to the end of humanity They are, however, far from infallible, and come with undesirable side-effects: reproduction of stereotypes, disclosure of confidential information, violation of intellectual property rights, and so on They open up new possibilities for malicious acts, particularly cyber-attacks and disinformation They are a source of systemic risk, particularly in terms of the potential for technological concentration in the hands of a small number of countries, companies or individuals Faced with these major challenges, we cannot repeat the mistakes of the past.",rule_candidate,information,choice|information,2,0,0,1,1,0,0,0,0,0,,,,,,
932e5524cf150c66,318795,"Our use of software to apply masks to face images has the following advantages: it allows very rapid characterization of the effect of masks on face recognition; it allows controlled exploration of factors such as mask size, shape, and color; it affords repeatability, which is key to the fair comparison of algorithms; it scales to very large datasets - in our study, some 6.2 million photographs - which allows fine-grained characterization of false positive rates in addition to false negative rates.",Our use of software to apply masks to face images,explicit,allows,permission,has the following advantages,,algorithms,True,"Our use of software to apply masks to face images has the following advantages: it allows very rapid characterization of the effect of masks on face recognition; it allows controlled exploration of factors such as mask size, shape, and color; it affords repeatability, which is key to the fair comparison of algorithms; it scales to very large datasets - in our study, some 6.2 million photographs - which allows fine-grained characterization of false positive rates in addition to false negative rates.",rule_candidate,payoff,choice|payoff,2,0,0,1,0,0,0,1,0,0,,,,,,
