ee0d622458825bd4,452720,"From our position, we must ensure that people have sufficient education to understand the importance of protecting their data; so that they are alert to the deceptions that exist in electronic media; and have the assurance that there are mechanisms to report and sanction bad practices and",we,explicit,must,obligation,ensure,,data,True,"From our position, we must ensure that people have sufficient education to understand the importance of protecting their data; so that they are alert to the deceptions that exist in electronic media; and have the assurance that there are mechanisms to report and sanction bad practices and",rule_candidate,payoff,choice|information|payoff,3,0,0,1,1,0,0,1,0,0,,,,,,
ee0d622458825bd4,452740,"These aspects can be addressed from a preventive or reactive approach ; that is, educating, raising awareness and providing tools to minimize the risks, threats and vulnerabilities that may occur in electronic media, as well as inhibiting behaviors that could generate impacts on the legal sphere of the holders through the establishment of sanctions of various kinds, as a consequence of acts or omissions that 149 In this situation, both the General Law on the Protection of Personal Data Held by Obligated Subjects and the Federal Law on the Protection of Personal Data Held by Private Parties and the regulations derived from them contemplate the existence of a duty of security, according to which those responsible for the treatment must take into account a series of factors and carry out various actions for the establishment and implementation of security measures that allow the protection of personal data against damage, loss, alteration, destruction, use, access or unauthorized treatment.",These aspects,explicit,can,permission,addressed,,tools,True,"These aspects can be addressed from a preventive or reactive approach ; that is, educating, raising awareness and providing tools to minimize the risks, threats and vulnerabilities that may occur in electronic media, as well as inhibiting behaviors that could generate impacts on the legal sphere of the holders through the establishment of sanctions of various kinds, as a consequence of acts or omissions that 149 In this situation, both the General Law on the Protection of Personal Data Held by Obligated Subjects and the Federal Law on the Protection of Personal Data Held by Private Parties and the regulations derived from them contemplate the existence of a duty of security, according to which those responsible for the treatment must take into account a series of factors and carry out various actions for the establishment and implementation of security measures that allow the protection of personal data against damage, loss, alteration, destruction, use, access or unauthorized treatment.",rule_candidate,payoff,choice|payoff,2,0,0,1,0,0,0,1,0,0,,,,,,
