ee0d622458825bd4,453123,"The Privacy Route reflects how, together, institutions, owners and those responsible can raise awareness levels regarding the value of the information to which we allow access in exchange for the use of information technologies and the services they provide and thereby meet our needs, without losing sight of the value of each piece of data, record, and information that, even if minimal, generates profits with its storage and distribution to those responsible for possessing it.","institutions , owners and those responsible",explicit,can,permission,raise awareness levels,,services,True,This leads to greater violations and less effectiveness of the regulatory mechanisms that allow for effective protection.,rule_candidate,information,choice|information|position,3,0,1,1,1,0,0,0,0,0,,,,,,
