efcb0d9a4b7f76d4,456188,"For more information, see: https://larepublica.pe/tecnologia/2020/10/17/ucloud-net-peruvian-project-seeks-to- connect-and-educate-the-most-distant-communities-in-the-country-video/ 3.2 Key concepts 3.2.1 Conceptual model of digital transformation However, as this is an emerging and disruptive issue, which generates uncertainty and mistrust, which obviously results in obstacles and challenges that must be overcome, the government must play a driving, articulating, facilitating and regulating role that aims at the synergy of all the actors involved in this transformative process.",that,explicit,must,obligation,overcome,,model,True,"For more information, see: https://larepublica.pe/tecnologia/2020/10/17/ucloud-net-peruvian-project-seeks-to- connect-and-educate-the-most-distant-communities-in-the-country-video/ 3.2 Key concepts 3.2.1 Conceptual model of digital transformation However, as this is an emerging and disruptive issue, which generates uncertainty and mistrust, which obviously results in obstacles and challenges that must be overcome, the government must play a driving, articulating, facilitating and regulating role that aims at the synergy of all the actors involved in this transformative process.",rule_candidate,information,choice|information|scope,3,0,0,1,1,1,0,0,0,0,,,,,,
