efcb0d9a4b7f76d4,457683,"In this regard, it should also be noted that the State has been laying the foundations for achieving transparency, accountability and efficiency of public spending that results in the improvement of the services demanded by citizens, which serves as support for this alternative solution; these foundations can be observed in: 180 Granickas, K. (2013).",it,explicit,should,obligation,noted|demanded,In this regard,services,True,"In this regard, it should also be noted that the State has been laying the foundations for achieving transparency, accountability and efficiency of public spending that results in the improvement of the services demanded by citizens, which serves as support for this alternative solution; these foundations can be observed in: 180 Granickas, K. (2013).",rule_candidate,information,choice|information,2,0,0,1,1,0,0,0,0,0,,,,,,
