f832f3024543ddf3,470266,"Article 36 1-In cases that are not covered in Article (35) herein and without prejudice to any harsher penalty stipulated in another law, a warning or a fine not exceeding (five million) Riyals shall be imposed on every person with a special natural or legal capacity - covered by the provisions of the Law - who violates any of the provisions of the Law or the Regulations.","Article 36 1 - In cases that are not covered in Article ( 35 ) herein and without prejudice to any harsher penalty stipulated in another law , a warning or a fine not exceeding ( five million ) Riyals",explicit,shall,obligation,imposed,with a special natural or legal capacity - covered by the provisions of the Law - who violates any of the provisions of the Law or the Regulations,,True,"Article 36 1-In cases that are not covered in Article (35) herein and without prejudice to any harsher penalty stipulated in another law, a warning or a fine not exceeding (five million) Riyals shall be imposed on every person with a special natural or legal capacity - covered by the provisions of the Law - who violates any of the provisions of the Law or the Regulations.",rule_candidate,payoff,choice|payoff,2,0,0,1,0,0,0,1,0,0,,,,,,
f832f3024543ddf3,470267,"The fine penalty may be doubled in the event of a repeat violation, even if it results in exceeding its maximum limit, provided that it does not exceed double this limit.",The fine penalty,explicit,may,permission,doubled,even if it results in exceeding its maximum limit|in the event of a repeat violation,,True,"The fine penalty may be doubled in the event of a repeat violation, even if it results in exceeding its maximum limit, provided that it does not exceed double this limit.",rule_candidate,payoff,choice|payoff|scope,3,0,0,1,0,1,0,1,0,0,,,,,,
