d the costs of publishing research results in peer -reviewed (International Scientific Indexing (ISI) journals with a non -zero impact-factor of Web of Science Core Collection and/or journals indexed in Scopus with a percentile of at least 25%.",rule_candidate,boundary,boundary|choice|payoff,3,1,0,1,0,0,0,1,0,0,,,,,,
